
Package Install
---------------

Arch packages are also available at:

https://github.com/kata198/pacman-utils-pkg       - Core package

https://github.com/kata198/pacman-utils-data-pkg  - The data


"extras" are not included yet in a package.


Manual Install
--------------

To install programs:

    ./install.sh  # as root, install to /usr/bin

    ./install.sh DESTDIR=$pkgdir  # Install to "$pkgdir"/usr/bin

    ./install.sh PREFIX=$HOME     # Install to $HOME/bin

To install data:

    ./install_data.sh # as root

To insall extras:

    ./install_extras.sh # as root
